{"tid":467656,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[大國勃起] 疑不滿放假要回校　強國16歲仔捅死班主任","createTime":"2017-11-13T16:28:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T17:07:47.000Z","uid":43189,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b0d8eb68df38c4426f814f2f40256cd183ead1e0","tid":467656,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T16:28:45.000Z","msg":"湖南沅江市周日（12日）發生校園兇殺案，沅江市第三中學一名16歲羅姓男學生與47歲鮑姓班主任當天下午發生爭執，未料羅男突然掏出一把匕首，瘋狂刺向班主任。鮑男隨即被送往醫院搶救，惟最終仍告不治。目前羅男已被警方控制，案件正在偵辦中。 <br />\n<br />\n經初步了解，事發當天學校放假，但鮑男要其中一班的學生回校寫作業，而羅男則因而與班主任在教員室發生爭執，期間羅男拿出匕首狂刺班主任的頸部，導致對方失血過多，送院搶救後不治。 <br />\n<br />\n事發後當地政府要求公安部門盡快破案及公布事件結果，依法依規處理；要求教育部門及各間學校要加強學生法制教育及心理輔導，同時加強安全防範及監管，以防再發生同類型事件。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20171113/mobile/bkncn-20171113040847376-1113_05011_001.html?refer=hn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171113%2Fmobile%2Fbkncn-20171113040847376-1113_05011_001.html%3Frefer%3Dhn&d=RPK1G0yWOc9aoPi5Txb6Zmxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=3e00ce29\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20171113/mobile/bkncn-20171113040847376-1113_05011_001.html?refer=hn</a>"},{"pid":"f4a55b5ccc86552dadeab4050d3d2eacea3864c4","tid":467656,"uid":22858,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T16:30:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>樓主個名真係嚇一嚇</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13dcd682b0b12cb1441db675b79c6b1b98373f7d","tid":467656,"uid":43189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T16:34:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>樓主個名真係嚇一嚇</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n追捕兩米黑鬼's style<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c064f272c1ad6238e37375a3315075df60e0379","tid":467656,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit